{{!< default}}

{{!-- ===== HERO (Circuit fan-out) ===== --}}
<section class="hero hero-circuit">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-content">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          {{!-- Eyebrow pill --}}
          <div class="hero-eyebrow">
            <span class="hero-eyebrow-dot" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7l1-8z" fill="#4f86ff"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="mono hero-eyebrow-text">WORKFLOW AUTOMATION FOR SMBs</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-headline">Get Your <span class="hero-grad">Time</span> Back</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">We build <strong class="hero-strong">automated workflows</strong> that cut admin, reduce errors, and free your team to focus on real work.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-primary-gradient">
              <span>Book a Discovery Call</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow-circle" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </span>
            </a>
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/services/" class="btn btn-secondary btn-ghost-arrow">
              <span>See What We Automate</span>
              <svg class="btn-arrow" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          {{!-- Eyebrow pill FR --}}
          <div class="hero-eyebrow">
            <span class="hero-eyebrow-dot" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7l1-8z" fill="#4f86ff"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="mono hero-eyebrow-text">AUTOMATISATION DE WORKFLOWS POUR PME</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-headline">Reprenez le contrôle de votre <span class="hero-grad">temps</span></h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">On met en place des <strong class="hero-strong">workflows automatisés</strong> qui réduisent l'admin, limitent les erreurs et redonnent du temps à votre équipe.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-primary-gradient">
              <span>Réserver un appel découverte</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow-circle" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </span>
            </a>
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/services/" class="btn btn-secondary btn-ghost-arrow">
              <span>Voir ce qu'on automatise</span>
              <svg class="btn-arrow" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        {{/match}}
      </div>

      {{!-- Circuit fan-out visual --}}
      <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="circuit-frame">
          <div class="circuit-frame-glow"></div>
          <div class="circuit-frame-inner">
            <div class="circuit-header">
              <span class="circuit-status mono">
                <span class="circuit-status-dot"></span>
                {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}running{{else}}en cours{{/match}}
              </span>
            </div>

            <div class="circuit-stage">
              {{!-- SVG overlay: trunk + fan curves + traveling packets --}}
              <svg class="circuit-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="wireC" x1="0" x2="1">
                    <stop offset="0" stop-color="#4f86ff"/>
                    <stop offset="1" stop-color="#34d399"/>
                  </linearGradient>
                  <filter id="glowC" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%">
                    <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="0.6"/>
                    <feMerge><feMergeNode/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
                  </filter>
                </defs>

                {{!-- Trunk: source right edge (32) -> fan point (40) --}}
                <path d="M 32 50 H 40" stroke="url(#wireC)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" filter="url(#glowC)" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>

                {{!-- Fan curves to ty = 14, 38, 62, 86 --}}
                <path d="M 40 50 C 48 50, 48 14, 56 14" stroke="url(#wireC)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" filter="url(#glowC)" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
                <path d="M 40 50 C 48 50, 48 38, 56 38" stroke="url(#wireC)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" filter="url(#glowC)" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
                <path d="M 40 50 C 48 50, 48 62, 56 62" stroke="url(#wireC)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" filter="url(#glowC)" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
                <path d="M 40 50 C 48 50, 48 86, 56 86" stroke="url(#wireC)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" filter="url(#glowC)" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>

                {{!-- Connection dots at card left edges --}}
                <circle cx="56" cy="14" r="0.8" fill="#34d399" filter="url(#glowC)"/>
                <circle cx="56" cy="38" r="0.8" fill="#34d399" filter="url(#glowC)"/>
                <circle cx="56" cy="62" r="0.8" fill="#34d399" filter="url(#glowC)"/>
                <circle cx="56" cy="86" r="0.8" fill="#34d399" filter="url(#glowC)"/>

                {{!-- Traveling packets --}}
                <g class="circuit-packets">
                  <circle r="0.7" fill="#9ef4cc">
                    <animateMotion dur="2.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" begin="0s"
                      path="M 32 50 H 40 C 48 50, 48 14, 56 14"/>
                  </circle>
                  <circle r="0.7" fill="#9ef4cc">
                    <animateMotion dur="2.95s" repeatCount="indefinite" begin="0.4s"
                      path="M 32 50 H 40 C 48 50, 48 38, 56 38"/>
                  </circle>
                  <circle r="0.7" fill="#9ef4cc">
                    <animateMotion dur="3.3s" repeatCount="indefinite" begin="0.8s"
                      path="M 32 50 H 40 C 48 50, 48 62, 56 62"/>
                  </circle>
                  <circle r="0.7" fill="#9ef4cc">
                    <animateMotion dur="3.65s" repeatCount="indefinite" begin="1.2s"
                      path="M 32 50 H 40 C 48 50, 48 86, 56 86"/>
                  </circle>
                </g>
              </svg>

              {{!-- Source (trigger) card --}}
              <div class="circuit-source">
                <div class="circuit-source-label mono">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}TRIGGER{{else}}DÉCLENCHEUR{{/match}}</div>
                <div class="circuit-source-body">
                  <span class="circuit-icon-tile circuit-icon-blue">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="13" height="13" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="12" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M4 8l8 5.5L20 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  </span>
                  <div class="circuit-source-text">
                    {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
                      <div class="circuit-source-title">New client</div>
                      <div class="circuit-source-sub mono">signs up</div>
                    {{else}}
                      <div class="circuit-source-title">Nouveau client</div>
                      <div class="circuit-source-sub mono">s'inscrit</div>
                    {{/match}}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              {{!-- Terminal cards --}}
              <div class="circuit-term" style="top:14%">
                <span class="circuit-icon-tile circuit-icon-green">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="12" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M4 8l8 5.5L20 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="circuit-term-label">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}Email reply{{else}}Réponse courriel{{/match}}</span>
                <span class="circuit-term-done mono">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}DONE{{else}}FAIT{{/match}}</span>
              </div>

              <div class="circuit-term" style="top:38%">
                <span class="circuit-icon-tile circuit-icon-green">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none"><rect x="3.5" y="5.5" width="17" height="15" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M3.5 10h17M8 4v3M16 4v3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="circuit-term-label">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}Calendar booked{{else}}Agenda réservé{{/match}}</span>
                <span class="circuit-term-done mono">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}DONE{{else}}FAIT{{/match}}</span>
              </div>

              <div class="circuit-term" style="top:62%">
                <span class="circuit-icon-tile circuit-icon-green">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none"><path d="M6 3h8l4 4v14H6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M14 3v4h4M9 12h6M9 16h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="circuit-term-label">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}Docs sent{{else}}Docs envoyés{{/match}}</span>
                <span class="circuit-term-done mono">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}DONE{{else}}FAIT{{/match}}</span>
              </div>

              <div class="circuit-term" style="top:86%">
                <span class="circuit-icon-tile circuit-icon-green">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none"><ellipse cx="12" cy="6" rx="7" ry="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M5 6v12c0 1.4 3.1 2.5 7 2.5s7-1.1 7-2.5V6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M5 12c0 1.4 3.1 2.5 7 2.5s7-1.1 7-2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="circuit-term-label">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}CRM updated{{else}}CRM mis à jour{{/match}}</span>
                <span class="circuit-term-done mono">{{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}DONE{{else}}FAIT{{/match}}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{{!-- ===== PAIN POINTS ===== --}}
<section class="section pain-redesign wash-orange" id="problems">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pain-redesign-grid">
      <div class="pain-redesign-intro">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          <p class="section-label">Sound familiar?</p>
          <h2 class="pain-redesign-title">Too much work still runs manually.</h2>
        {{else}}
          <p class="section-label">Ça vous parle?</p>
          <h2 class="pain-redesign-title">Trop de travail se fait encore à la main.</h2>
        {{/match}}
      </div>
      <div class="pain-redesign-list" aria-label="Common business pain points">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">01</span>
            <p>Client info gets entered into three different systems. Orders get copy-pasted between tools, and someone rebuilds the same Friday report every week.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">02</span>
            <p>A new hire starts, and setup still takes two weeks. Accounts, permissions, docs, and introductions all need a senior person to walk them through.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">03</span>
            <p>Approvals sit in email for days, so quotes go out late and invoices get missed. The process breaks because it depends on people remembering.</p>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">01</span>
            <p>Les infos clients sont saisies dans trois systèmes différents. Les commandes sont copiées d'un outil à l'autre, et quelqu'un refait le même rapport du vendredi chaque semaine.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">02</span>
            <p>Une nouvelle recrue arrive, et le démarrage prend encore deux semaines. Comptes, accès, documentation et présentations demandent chaque fois l'aide d'une personne senior.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">03</span>
            <p>Les approbations restent des jours dans les courriels, alors les devis partent en retard et des factures passent à l'oubli. Le processus lâche parce qu'il dépend de ce que les gens pensent à faire.</p>
          </div>
        {{/match}}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

